Beat cream cheese and 1/4 cup of the milk in large bowl with wire whisk until well blended. Add remaining 1 cup milk and pudding mix. Beat with wire whisk 1 minute. Gently stir in whipped topping until well blended. Spoon into crust. Refrigerate 4 hours or until set. Garnish with chocolate curls made with BAKER'S Premium White Baking Chocolate. Store leftover pie in refrigerator.